resources_ideas_theme_4: Mapeamento aberto
---
resources_ideas_theme_4_text:

Saiba mais sobre o mapeamento aberto pelos sites da [Mapbox](https://www.mapbox.com), [OpenStreetMap](https://www.openstreetmap.org/) e [Humanitarian OpenStreetMap](https://www.hotosm.org/).

